  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Animal
    Represents an Animal, with health and happiness levels.
    AnimalFarm
    An animal farm.
    AnimalTest  
    Asset
    Basic "asset" that can be purchased or sold in the store, or used by the player on the farm.
    Carrot
    Represents a carrot.
    ChemicalSpray
    Chemical Spray - an item used on crops to speed up harvest by 4 days.
    Compost
    Compost - an item used on crops to speed up harvest by 2 days.
    Cow
    A cow.
    Crop
    Represents a crop.
    CropCareGUI
    GUI window for tending to crops.
    Farm
    Represents a Farm.
    Farmer
    Handles daily actions made to the farm by the player.
    FarmGUI
    Main GUI window for the farm simulator, with buttons that lead to daily actions or other actions a player can perform.
    FeedingGUI
    GUI window for handling the feeding of item(s) to animals.
    Fox
    A fox.
    GameManager
    Class that essentially runs the entire GUI game by handling the creation and removal of GUI windows.
    Hipotke
    Represents Hipotke Grass, a reference to the series That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime.
    InstantGrowLite
    Instant-Grow Lite(R), used to halve time required to harvest.
    InstantGrowPro
    Instant-Grow Pro(R) - instantly readies a crop type (e.g.
    Item
    A child class of asset which can be bought from stores and consumed for player benefit.
    MoomooFarm
    Moo Moo Farm - a farm powered by cows.
    Mushroom
    Represents mushroom, a type of crop.
    PandaGummy
    Panda Gummy - feed to animals to boost double the health of Stockfeed.
    SetupGUI
    GUI window for setting up the player's farm, farmer and game duration.
    Sheep
    A sheep.
    Stockfeed
    Stockfeed - feed to animals to boost health!
    StoreGUI
    GUI window for purchasing from the general county store.
    Tomacco
    Represents Tomacco, which is a solid mid-range crop.
    TomaccoLand
    Tomacco Land, a type of farm.
    TrumpRanch
    Trump Ranch - the name says it all.
    Wasabi
    Wasabi, a type of crop.
    Wheat
    The wheat crop, which is the cheapest crop available in-game.
